flowchart LR
    A[Customer browses products/services] --> B[Adds items to Cart]
    B --> C[Reviews Cart: items, prices, totals]
    C --> D[Clicks Checkout]
    D --> E[Enters contact & delivery details]
    E --> F[Chooses payment method]
    F --> G[Reviews final order summary]
    G --> H[Confirms payment]
    H --> I{Payment result}
    I -->|Success| J[Order confirmed<br/>Order number generated]
    I -->|Failure| F2[Show error & allow retry]

    J --> K[Stock reserved / updated]
    K --> L[Confirmation email/SMS sent]
    L --> M[Operations team prepares order]
    M --> N[Order shipped / service delivered]
    N --> O[Customer sees status & history<br/>Optionally gives feedback]
